    {
      "id": 12,
      "date": "2022-01-30T12:02:16+08:00",
      "author": "Micraow",
      "url": "",
      "text": "用grub引导的机子，要用以下命令重新安装grub\n\n/usr/share/grub/sbat.csv在启用模块的情况下重新安装 GRUB TPM并签名：\n\n```bash\ngrub-install --target=x86_64-efi --efi-directory=esp --modules=\"tpm\" --sbat /usr/share/grub/sbat.csv\nsbsign --key MOK.key --cert MOK.crt --output esp/EFI/GRUB/grubx64.efi esp/EFI/GRUB/grubx64.efi\ncp esp/GRUB/grubx64.efi esp/boot/grubx64.efi\n```\n\nesp是引导器分区，通常是/boot",
      "parent": 0,
      "reply_to": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "date": "2022-01-30T12:02:47+08:00",
      "author": "Micraow",
      "url": "",
      "text": "参考archwiki:\n\nhttps://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Unified_Extensible_Firmware_Interface/Secure_Boot",
      "parent": 12,
      "reply_to": "Micraow"
    }
  ],
